OL,3,CDonald Trump or Kamala Harris? The big
OL,4,Cquestion for a Welsh farmer
OL,6,FNot every Carmarthenshire farmer must
OL,7,Fchoose between Kamala Harris or Donald
OL,8,FTrump on 5 November, but that's the
OL,9,Fbig question facing Welshman Elfryn
OL,10,FThomas.
OL,12,FElfryn, 47, spent his childhood on his
OL,13,Fgrandparents' farm in Llanllwni,
OL,14,FCarmarthenshire, but now, Phoenix,
OL,15,FArizona, is his home.
