OL,3,CDonald Trump or Kamala Harris? The big
OL,4,Cquestion for a Welsh farmer
OL,6,FThe state in the south-west of the
OL,7,FUnited States is 14 times the size of
OL,8,FWales, and is a battleground state in
OL,9,Fthe Presidential Election between the
OL,10,FRepublican candidate Donald Trump and
OL,11,FDemocratic candidate Kamala Harris.
OL,13,F"I'd been at the Agricultural College
OL,14,Fin Aberystwyth, and Wisconsin was the
OL,15,Fdairy capital of the world at the
OL,16,Ftime," Elfryn told Sion Jenkins in
OL,17,FMonday's special episode of Y Byd ar
OL,18,FBedwar on S4C.
