OL,3,CDonald Trump or Kamala Harris? The big
OL,4,Cquestion for a Welsh farmer
OL,6,F"It was my grandfather's dream to come
OL,7,Fout to America, so he came out here
OL,8,Fthrough me then."
OL,10,FElfryn is married to Tami and they
OL,11,Fhave four children. In 2015 he gave up
OL,12,Fhis dream of becoming a dairy farmer
OL,13,Fand moved to Phoenix to run the family
OL,14,Fcar company.
OL,16,FWith the future and success of his
OL,17,Fbusiness a top priority, Elfryn
OL,18,Fbelieves former president Donald Trump
OL,19,Fis the best person to run the country
OL,20,Fwhen it comes to the economy.
