OL,3,CDonald Trump or Kamala Harris? The big
OL,4,Cquestion for a Welsh farmer
OL,6,F"He's a better businessman," Elfryn
OL,7,Fsays. "When he was president before,
OL,8,Feveryone's business succeeded. The
OL,9,Fprices of milk, eggs and bread were a
OL,10,Flot less, and now they just have...
OL,11,Fwell, they've tripled! Trump wasn't a
OL,12,Fpolitician when he came in as
OL,13,Fpresident ` he was a businessman."
OL,15,FThis will be the second time Elfryn
OL,16,Fhas voted in a Presidential Election
OL,17,Fafter becoming an American citizen in
OL,18,F2020. He has already experienced the
OL,19,Fpolitical rifts which exist in the
OL,20,Fcountry, even at home with his wife,
OL,21,FTami, who is a registered Democrat.
