OL,3,CDonald Trump or Kamala Harris? The big
OL,4,Cquestion for a Welsh farmer
OL,6,FWith the married couple raising a
OL,7,Fteenage daughter, protecting women's
OL,8,Frights is important to Elfryn and
OL,9,FTami. While Elfryn feels that current
OL,10,FVice-President Kamala Harris would do
OL,11,Fthe best job of ensuring that, he has
OL,12,Fhis doubts.
OL,14,F"I think she's more genuine than
OL,15,FTrump, but I'm not sure she's the
OL,16,Fperson who's going to be able to turn
OL,17,Fthe country back the way it was.
OL,18,FTrump, I see, is the guy who can do
OL,19,Fsomething like that," he explained.
