OL,6,FAnother concern Elfryn has is
OL,7,Fimmigration. Arizona shares a 400-mile
OL,8,Fborder with Mexico, and immigration is
OL,9,Fone of the most important topics for
OL,10,FArizonans in the election. Once again,
OL,11,Fit's his daughter's safety which is on
OL,12,Fhis mind when confronted with the
OL,13,Fsubject.
