OL,6,F"With young children, it's scary for
OL,7,Feveryone here, especially young girls.
OL,8,FThere are some places we don't let
OL,9,FAriana go. Sex trafficking is awful
OL,10,Fhere; drug trafficking is awful here;
OL,11,Fdrug cartels - they run back and forth
OL,12,Fthrough Arizona all the time. It's
OL,13,Fscary."
OL,15,FDonald Trump has promised mass
OL,16,Fdeportations of those living in the US
OL,17,Fillegally, while Kamala Harris has
OL,18,Fsaid she will punish those who
OL,19,Fcontinue to cross the border without
OL,20,Fpermission to do so.
