OL,3,CDonald Trump or Kamala Harris? The big
OL,4,Cquestion for a Welsh farmer
OL,6,FThe race between Donald Trump and
OL,7,FKamala Harris is expected to be
OL,8,Fhistorically close, with the outcome
OL,9,Fdependent on a handful of swing states
OL,10,Fwhich could vote either way. Those
OL,11,Fseven states are Arizona, Georgia,
OL,12,FMichigan, Nevada, North Carolina,
OL,13,FPennsylvania and Wisconsin.
OL,15,FJoe Biden narrowly won Arizona in 2020
OL,16,Fwith around 11,000 more votes than
OL,17,FDonald Trump. When 150million
OL,18,FAmericans will turn up at ballot boxes
OL,19,Fon the morning of 5 November, 2024,
OL,20,Fthe vote of undecided voters like
OL,21,FElfryn will be crucial.
